___TESTS___

scenarios:
- name: Injects widget with cbid and sets global default
  code: |-
    const mockData = { cbid: 'demo-uuid', consentModeEnabled: true, waitForUpdate: 2000, regionSettings: [] };
    runCode(mockData);
    assertApi('setDefaultConsentState').wasCalled();
    assertApi('injectScript').wasCalled();
- name: Consent Mode disabled skips defaults
  code: |-
    const mockData = { cbid: 'demo-uuid', consentModeEnabled: false };
    runCode(mockData);
    assertApi('setDefaultConsentState').wasNotCalled();
    assertApi('injectScript').wasCalled();


___NOTES___

Master of Cookies CMP — loads the shared banner from cdn.masterofcookies.eu and
sets synchronous denied defaults for Google Consent Mode v2 (timing safeguard).
Per-region defaults are supported via the Default Consent State table.
Place the tag on the "Consent Initialization - All Pages" trigger.
